    <item>
      <title>响尾蛇启动债券发售，为奋进收购提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/diamondback-kicks-off-bond-sale-to-help-fund-endeavor-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Diamondback Energy Inc. 正在通过发行债券进军美国投资级市场，为其以 260 亿美元收购 Endeavor Energy Resources LP 提供部分资金，与其他蓝筹公司一道，利用强劲的投资者需求进行与收购相关的债务交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/diamondback-kicks-off-bond-sale-to-help-fund-endeavor-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦央行寻求打破贷方对支付的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/kazakh-central-bank-seeks-to-break-two-lenders-grip-on-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦央行希望通过明年初引入一个新系统来促进普遍准入的交易，从而削弱该国最大的两家银行对支付的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/kazakh-central-bank-seeks-to-break-two-lenders-grip-on-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙紧张局势升级，土耳其和以色列交换贸易威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/turkey-restricts-exports-to-israel-over-gaza-air-drop-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其因反对以色列放弃对加沙地带援助的提议而决定限制对以色列的出口，此举引起了迅速的报复性反应，进一步加剧了这两个曾经的军事盟友之间本已紧张的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/turkey-restricts-exports-to-israel-over-gaza-air-drop-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
